</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_533" id="265v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_533_r1l1">Der Stat ʒu Holuelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_533_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>Fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als wır rechtes ʒu dem Jobs Peler der bey eẅch in fenknuſſ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l3"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> gſcholl ıſt vnd auch <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> peler </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l4">von 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſuchen</expan></del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd des Lands notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vor <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l7"><expan>ʒuv<ex>er</ex>ſuchen</expan> . etwıeoft begert vnd gemant <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_533_line_1592203350528_2053">auch nu </ab></add> ʒugeſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l8">vnd ein rechttag / auf den <expan>freıt<ex>ag</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt vor <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> tag geſecʒt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l9">ıſt Alſo <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd manen wır eẅr <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l10">Jr den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe wır darauf / ʒu eẅch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gefertıgt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l11"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> / ʒu <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Jobs Pelers <expan>ernſtlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſuchung</expan> / vnd auch rechtes </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l12">auf den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag ʒu Jm <expan>ʒuhelff<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fleıſʒ <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd guten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l13"><expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> alſo beweıſet vnd tuet . Damıt dıe ſache geendet vnd den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l14"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darein niht getragen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . als etc . das wellen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_533_r1l15"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_533" id="265v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat zu Holvelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir rechtes zu dem Jobs Peler, der bey
                        ewch in fenknuss <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>recht<ex>er</ex></expan> gscholl ist, und auch
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Peler von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und des lands notdurft
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vor <expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>suchen</expan> etwieoft begert und gemant
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> uns
                            <add>auch nu</add> zugesagt und ein rechttag auf den
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>freit<ex>ag</ex></expan> schierist vor
                            <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> tag</q>30.10.1422</note></app> geseczt ist, also
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                        manen wir ewr <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                        <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die wir darauf zu ewch
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gefertigt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        Jobs Pelers <expan>ernstlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>suchung</expan> und auch rechtes auf den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> tag zu im <expan>zu
                                helff<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> fleisz,
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und guten
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> also beweiset und tuet, damit die sache
                        geendet und den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> darein niht getragen
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, als etc. Das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
